Private Shared _hashtable As New System.Collections.Hashtable()
Function SetValue(ByVal id as String, ByVal value As String) As Object SyncLock _hashtable.SyncRoot dim Key as String = id + Report.Parameters!TableGuid.Value _hashtable(Key) = value End SyncLock End Function
Function GetValue(ByVal id as String) As Object SyncLock _hashtable.SyncRoot dim Key as String = id + Report.Parameters!TableGuid.Value Return _hashtable(Key ) End SyncLock End Function
Public Function GetGroupPageNumber (group as Object, pagenumber as Integer) as Object If Not (group = GetValue("CurrentGroup")) SetValue("Offset", pagenumber - 1) SetValue("CurrentGroup", group) End If Return pagenumber - GetValue("Offset") End Function
Public Function SetLabels(p_RptLiteralsPhoneNum as String, p_RptLiteralsFaxNum as String, p_RptLiteralsLNo as String, p_RptLiteralsLDate as String, p_RptLiteralsRptTitleRemit as String, p_RptLiteralsPage as String) as String SetValue("RptLiteralsPhoneNum", p_RptLiteralsPhoneNum) SetValue("RptLiteralsFaxNum", p_RptLiteralsFaxNum) SetValue("RptLiteralsLNo", p_RptLiteralsLNo) SetValue("RptLiteralsLDate", p_RptLiteralsLDate) SetValue("RptLiteralsRptTitleRemit", p_RptLiteralsRptTitleRemit) SetValue("RptLiteralsPage", p_RptLiteralsPage) Return "" End Function
